Hello <%= @leave_request.approver.full_name %>,

<% if @leave_request.captured? %>
<%= @leave_request.captured_by.full_name %> has captured <%= @leave_request.leave_type.to_s.downcase %> leave for <%= @leave_request.employee.full_name %>.
<% else %>
<%= @leave_request.employee.full_name %> has applied for <%= @leave_request.leave_type.to_s.downcase %> leave.
<% end %>

<%= render :partial => 'leave_details' %>
<%= render :partial => 'leave_balance' %>

To approve or decline the leave request, please follow this link:

  <%= leave_request_url(@leave_request, :tenant => @account.subdomain) %>
  
Thank You.

